short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Kattis Submission Tracker for BYU CPC

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This browser extension is used by the BYU Competitive Programming Club to track their submissions and practice. The extension collects submissions and sends them to the BYU CPC Leaderboard website.
